          </a>
          <a href="/blog/scrabble-and-memory-training/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
            <span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble and Memory Training</span>
          </a>
        
          <a href="/blog/scrabble-memory-techniques/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Memory Techniques</span></a>
</div>
      </aside>

      <div class="not-prose mt-10 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-blue-800/20 border border-blue-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-medium">🔍 Expand your vocabulary with our free Scrabble Word Finder — discover new words instantly</p>
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-400 text-gray-950 text-sm font-semibold transition-colors">Open Word Finder →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/blog/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Back to all articles</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
